follows player when these items are held:=sledi igralcu, ko ta drži naslednje predmete:

A transparent block, basically empty space. It is usually left behind after digging something.=Prosojen blok, v bistvu prazen prostor. Običajno ostane za nečim, kar izkopljete.

Whenever you are not wielding any item, you use the hand which acts as a tool with its own capabilities. When you are wielding an item which is not a mining tool or a weapon it will behave as if it would be the hand.=Kadar koli v roki ne držite nobenega predmeta, uporabljate roko, ki deluje kot orodje z lastnimi zmožnostmi. Ko držite predmet, ki ni orodje za rudarjenje ali orožje, se bo ta obnašal kot roka.



